      <content><![CDATA[<p>Contents can be located in the <em>/.content/</em> folder of a site or sub-site. The example shows the content types of this Mercury demo site.</p>
<pre>GET <a title="Content Folder Request" href="%(link0)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">/json/sites/default/mercury-demo/.content/</a>
{
  "article-m": {},
  "contact-m": {},
  "decoy-m": {},
  "event-m": {},
  "faq-m": {},
  ...
}
</pre>]]></content>
